text: Castillon-de-Castets is a former commune. It is found in the region Nouvelle- Aquitaine in the Gironde department in the southwest of France. On 1 January 2017, it was merged into the new commune Castets et Castillon.Arrêté préfectoral 1 August 2016 == References == Category:Former communes in Gironde
title: Castillon-de-Castets
